# Testing Casadi

## Installing Casadi

1. `conda create -n casadi-test pip`
2. `conda install numpy scipy matplotlib`
3. `pip install casadi`

## Installing the optimal control code

1. From the project root (where pyproject.toml lives) run 
```pip install -e .```

2. (Optional) Verify the install 
```
python -c "import casadi_control; print('casadi_control imported successfully')"
```

## Running the examples

Navigate to the examples/ directory and run the python scripts.


